Run single SSH command that gathers all info:
```bash
ssh host 'echo "CORES:$(nproc)"; echo "MEM:$(free -g | awk "/Mem:/{print \$2}")"; echo "DISK:$(df -h /tmp | awk "NR==2{print \$4}")"; echo "RUST:$(rustc --version 2>/dev/null || echo none)"; echo "ARCH:$(uname -m)"'
